videos.description: Steve Kerr explains why the Warriors didn't deserve to win vs. the Clippers and how much Steph Curry's absence affects the team.
videos.headline: Kerr: 'Everything changes without Steph'

videos.description: A frustrated Klay Thompson breaks down the difference between the Clippers' defense and the Warriors' defense, while also discussing his off night shooting.
